content:
Based on the given factors, what are two comprehensive strategies that you can suggest to improve employee job satisfaction while considering a limited budget?
Here's a JSON data that includes relevant information on employee satisfaction factors:
{
   "factors":[
      {
         "name":"Workplace Culture",
         "description":"Company values and mission alignment"
      },
      {
         "name":"Communication",
         "description":"Effective communication with colleagues and superiors"
      },
      {
         "name":"Leadership",
         "description":"Clear direction and support from managers"
      },
      {
         "name":"Training and Development",
         "description":"Opportunities to improve skills and advance careers"
      },
      {
         "name":"Work-life Balance",
         "description":"Healthy balance between work and personal life"
      },
      {
         "name":"Recognition and Rewards",
         "description":"Acknowledgment and rewards for hard work"
      },
      {
         "name":"Alignment of Goals",
         "description":"Understanding of how work contributes to company success"
      }
   ]
}
Please suggest two innovative strategies that can improve employee job satisfaction while considering a limited budget, taking into account the factors mentioned above.
